    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say the second area's stability \"relies on the momentum of its current demographic shifts,\" are you implying that the lack of a long-standing demographic makes it more volatile? Like, does the rapid turnover and changing population actually act as a negative indicator for property value retention in the long run?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
